{"tid":667134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家D的士狗係咪真係唔撚識路","createTime":"2018-05-16T13:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T14:22:31.000Z","uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0285b9ebe848e0b8c85d02540b2df430b3dcf73","tid":667134,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"事源我平時都會的士番屋企<br />\n咁由旺角番我屋企基本上得一條路線<br />\n間唔中有司機唔識行 會行錯第二條路<br />\nD司機都會認錯，問我平時坐幾錢的士，然後收番果個數<br />\n<br />\n今日就撞著個司機 行錯路，我話行錯路，佢話無人會行我本身果條路線，大佬呀我一個月坐五十幾次的士番屋企會唔會唔知呀？ 我即刻話落車 ,然後嘈佢，話佢唔識路，點知佢仲死口話條路線岩<br />\n<br />\n我即刻塞500蚊比佢 叫佢起標，去兩條路線既分叉位行多次計幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n結果一條路60蚊一條路72蚊<br />\n<br />\n我落車就話 的士佬唔識路就咪學人揸車搵食啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fac332f3d37f7b7041a1aeb653be35809d5dda","tid":667134,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:22:31.000Z","msg":"型"}]}